data.description: Welcome to this Perfectly maintained private oasis with so much character. This property is country living but also a couple minutes away from town, best of both worlds. The home sits on over 2 acres with a three car detached garage and over 900 unfinished SQFT over top. Ionic above ground pool (chemical free). Two separate sheds that have electricity and attic space over top. The garage, Pool and all electrical outside the home have a separate breaker box. This is the perfect home to kick back and relax in your screened in porch with a beautiful large Deck, pool, grilling area, nature. The homeowners have kept the home in prestigious condition and you can feel the love that was put into it. The home is also equipped with whole house generator. Don't hesitate to call and schedule an appointment it will not last long.
